---
// Language redirect - instant via JavaScript, fallback via meta refresh
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Redirecting...</title>
  <meta http-equiv="refresh" content="0;url=/en/">
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://eflury.com/en/">
  <script>window.location.replace('/en/');</script>
</head>
<body>
  <a href="/en/">Redirecting to English...</a>
</body>
</html>
